## 7. Logging & Tracing

```typescript
import { createLogger } from '@zhop/logger'

const logger = createLogger('svc-astro')

// ✅ Structured logging
logger.info('Hehun computed', {
  person1Id: 'user123',
  person2Id: 'user456',
  score: 78,
  duration: 125,  // ms
})

// ❌ Don't
console.log('Score:', score)
```

